# Mi Tienda Digital

## Project Description
Mi Tienda Digital is an e-commerce platform designed to streamline the process of buying and selling products online. It offers a seamless experience for both buyers and sellers, enabling efficient transactions with various payment options.

## Features
- User-friendly interface
- Secure payment processing
- Inventory management for sellers
- Search functionality for products
- Order tracking system
- Customer reviews and ratings

## Categories
- Electronics
- Fashion
- Home & Garden
- Toys & Hobbies
- Health & Beauty
- Sports

## Installation Instructions
1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/socialmediasv-pixelCreame/mi-tienda-digital.git`
2. Install dependencies: `npm install`
3. Start the application: `npm start`
4. Access the app at `http://localhost:3000`.

